data.description: It's home sweet home in this spacious Lowcountry home adorned with quintessential double front porches! Nestled in the desirable, picturesque White Gables subdivision close to award-winning schools, shopping and dining, and historic downtown Summerville, this community has it all: a private pool with splash area, playground, tennis courts, clubhouse, and large community park areas.Beyond location, this home features all the space and comfort you could need. Downstairs features include an office with brand new built-in shelving, an oversized family room with gas fireplace, a huge kitchen with loads of storage and pantry, sunny eat-in breakfast area, powder room, full laundry room, and a separate dining or flex room. Upstairs you'll enjoy a large primary suite with garden tub and doublevanity, guest bath, and three bedrooms. Two bedrooms share an additional Jack and Jill bathroom with separate half baths in each room. Enjoy access to a secondary full porch upstairs. Outside, entertain guests under a beautiful pergola. Feel confident in your new home with brand new carpet, recent HVAC and water heater. Home is calling, so schedule your showing today.
